Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's still down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Choji keep him still like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I can only give\Nemergency first-aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But, who would've guessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that the original was hidden\Namong the clones.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not up to\NShikamaru's level...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess you're pretty smart, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't compare me with Shikamaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm impressed that you were able\N to fire off your new Jutsu three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even during training,\Ntwo was the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His quick thinking in making\N{\i1}his next move after failing only once...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His unshakable confidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto has truly become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfecting, to this level, {\i1}the Jutsu that\N even the Fourth Hokage {\i1}could not master...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like it's time to put\N{\i1}our trust in the next generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's surpassed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the one Naruto always\N{\i1}envisions before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are making him steadily stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't that so, Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, we should get going...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to\Nthe Hidden Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kakashi Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tying up loose ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I lose...\Nto young brats like you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're someone who's fought\Nagainst the First Hokage...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so we may seem like kids to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But to us,\Nyou're just a washed-up old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're near death\Nand groveling at our feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One after another,\Na new generation will succeed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The immediate danger has passed,\Nbut the Akatsuki still remain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not let down your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, those wounds are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my badge of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We did some emergency treatment...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case, get it checked thoroughly\Nat the Leaf Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I don't need...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take full responsibility\Nand take him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Got it, Naruto?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, I order you\Nto take a few days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest your minds and\Nyour bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean about Naruto's wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the Akatsuki corpse\Nthat Kakashi brought back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's already been sent\Nto the coroner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then send a message to\Nwhoever's in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it a top priority\Nand put a rush on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally over...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll part with you guys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But your house is this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuma Sarutobi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to be up and about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shikamaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your shogi partner is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You were Asuma's favorite,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so it will be lonely for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,From precious things to silly things...\Nhe taught me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shogi was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be lying if I said\NI didn't feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm no longer allowed\Nto act like a little kid ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't keep crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I always complain about\Nwhat a bother things are,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and because of that,\NI messed up a lot as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And each time,\NAsuma was there to protect me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,although he was such\Nan evasive and odd teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, he was a super cool grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why...\Nthis time it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When that child is born,\N it'll be my turn to be a protective teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've gotta become\Na cool grown-up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, Pops.\NUnlike Asuma, you're good...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...A Climbing Silver attack, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What you'd call a necessary sacrifice to\N protect the King against a higher opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you escape there,\Nthen a knight will come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So whichever the pawn runs to,\Nyour bishop will be supported...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, that knight sure is\Na nasty move there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're to compare a Hidden Leaf Ninja\N to shogi pieces, I'm a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuma said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Asuma knew\Nyour personality very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, who would be the King?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do you know who the King is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't it the Hokage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until recently, I thought so too...\N{\i1}But it wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the time comes,\N{\i1}you'll realize it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The children who will be taking over\Nthe future Hidden Leaf Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what it's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have enough power\Nto protect the King yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You better work harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so reckless...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so upset...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't talk back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Scrapes and bruises...\N{\i1}these injuries aren't too serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real problem is this arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's broken in several places.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His body isn't able to withstand {\i1}his Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the conclusion of\Nthe coroner's team about Kakuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Although they're not\Ncompletely finished yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we must notify\Nthe supervising Jonin about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Summon Kakashi and Yamato\Nto the coroner's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So Hidan and Kakuzu are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It seems they were killed\Nby Naruto's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought they would take down\Nanother Akatsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,if we let them live...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like it went quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure even the Akatsuki would never have\N expected to lose two of their members at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The autopsy is not complete yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But as we examined the corpse,\N we figured something out about Naruto's new Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The damage this fellow sustained was caused by\N something totally different from the usual barrage of hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Every Chakra Network connecting\Nhis body cells has been severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,His Chakra Network...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. A condition like this\Nis usually unimaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind Style: Rasen-Shuriken...\Nis this powerful...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than an offensive attack,\Nthis works more like poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A microscopic attack that inflicts\Ndamage at the cellular level...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm assuming that the Wind Chakra changed\N in Chakra Form into infinite small blades...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,attacking all the cells\Nwithin his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What a Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than the number of attacks,\N it should be described as a concentrated attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the user of the Jutsu, Naruto, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi... This new Jutsu...\NThe Wind Style: Rasen-Shuriken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Forbid Naruto from using it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that serious...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The same condition afflicts\NNaruto's right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it's not nearly\Nas bad as this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If he continues using\Nthis new Jutsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto will lose his ability\Nto mold Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,With such a powerful Jutsu,\Nthere's sure to be risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If the cells are disconnected from the body's Chakra Network,\N even my medical skills won't cure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Be certain to emphasize that\Nto Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:17:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Naruto. this new Jutsu.\N Use it only when absolutely necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do {\i1}not{\i0} use it too often!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NIf you can make it better-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Medical Ninjutsu cannot heal\Neverything right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But this kind of makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like you and I are\Ngetting closer to Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
